    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements with documented justification. Relative hemolysis index predictions agree with FDA benchmark data within 11.4% across all operating points, satisfying the 15% acceptance criterion. RH < 1 for all 5 flow-speed combinations relative to predicate device. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device submission.",
